<component type="desktop">
  <id>net.epson.epsonscan2</id>
  <name>Epson Scan 2</name>
  <summary>Software for Epson scanners &amp; multifunction printer.</summary>
  <developer_name>Seiko Epson Corporation</developer_name>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">net.epson.epsonscan2.desktop</launchable>
  <project_license>LGPL-2.1 AND LicenseRef-proprietary=http://download.ebz.epson.net/dsc/du/02/eula/global/LINUX_EN.html</project_license>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <description>
    <p>Epson Scan 2 is a scanning application for Epson scanner. It
    allows to set various scanner settings with graphical user
    interface and save the scanned images to the various file
    type.</p>
    <p>It supports USB, and network connection for the network capable
    scanners.</p>
    <p>Scanners can also be controlled with the command line.</p>
    <p>While the application is Free Software, the scanner drivers
    contains Proprietary components.</p>
    <p>This build is not supported by Epson Seiko Corporation, and is provided as is.</p>
  </description>
